descriptionHtml:
PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED A RIPP CITY FITNESS ACCOUNT TO ACCESS THIS APP. IF YOU'RE IN A CURRENT RIPP CITY FITNESS TRAINING PROGRAM YOULL GET IT FREE FROM OUR TEAM!

Begin your journey to a healthier lifestyle and let RIPP CITY Fitness help you along the way. Introducing the Fitness Tracker. The most comprehensive fitness platform with:
* Access your customized workout designed by Al Wilson
* Preset workouts and the option to create your own
* Track your daily fitness activities
* Track your weight and other body metrics
* Over 2000+ exercises and activities
* Clear 3D exercise demonstrations
* Over 150 badges to earn
* Stay connected to our fitness community

Select workouts online and synchronize them with your app to workout at home or in the gym while keeping track of your progress. From strength to weight lifting, this is like having Al Wilson guiding and giving you the motivation you need. Also check alwilsonfitness.com for many extra tools, such as your personal fitness profile, free nutrition plan, goal setting and much more!

descriptionHtml:
PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED A WILSON UNIVERSAL COACHING MEMBER ACCOUNT TO ACCESS THIS APP. ASK YOUR COACH OR VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO JOIN OUR ONLINE COMMUNITY AND GET THE SUPPORT YOU NEED!

Al C. Wilson, Life and Business Coach has created the Wilson Universal Coaching app to provide you with a supportive network of like-minded individuals and businesses, all driven by a common goal: to unleash their fullest potential. We provide an array of resources, from courses and events to webinars and fitness training, all tailored to help you overcome obstacles and find clarity on your path to success. This is the space where we conquer limitations, embrace growth, and turn obstacles into steppingstones.

The Wilson Universal Coaching mobile app is the most comprehensive online and mobile growth coaching platform with:

* Access to a wide variety of online courses and exclusive content
* Life Coaching resources
* Business Coaching resources
* Health and Fitness Coaching
* Join webinars and live events
* Track your progress regardless of your coaching path
* Earn certificates and badges for your progress
* Stay connected to our community

WELLNESS. GROWTH. RESULTS
